      <h3>üìÑ What is a PDF?</h3>
      <p>
        PDF (Portable Document Format) is a file format created by Adobe in 1993. It preserves document
        formatting across all devices and operating systems, making it the standard for sharing documents.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>üîí Why PDFs for Security?</h3>
