  <h2>Best Practices for PDF Management</h2>

  <h3>File Naming Conventions</h3>
  <p>Use descriptive names with dates and versions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>‚úÖ <code>2025-01-15_Contract_v2.pdf</code></li>
    <li>‚úÖ <code>Invoice_12345_ACME_Corp.pdf</code></li>
    <li>‚ùå <code>document1.pdf</code></li>
