  </ul>

  <h3>Backup Strategy</h3>
  <p>Always keep backups of important PDFs:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>3-2-1 Rule:</strong> 3 copies, on 2 different media types, with 1 offsite</li>
    <li>Use cloud storage (encrypted!) for offsite backups</li>
    <li>Test backups regularly‚Äîcan you actually restore them?</li>
  </ul>

