  <h2>Common PDF Problems &amp; Solutions</h2>

  <h3>Problem: PDF won't open</h3>
  <p><strong>Possible causes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>File is corrupted</li>
    <li>PDF is password-protected</li>
    <li>Incompatible PDF version</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Solutions:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Try opening in a different PDF viewer (Adobe Reader, Chrome, Firefox)</li>
    <li>Ask the sender for the password</li>
    <li>Re-download the file (may have been corrupted during download)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Problem: PDF is too large to email</h3>
  <p><strong>Email attachment limits:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Gmail: 25 MB</li>
    <li>Outlook: 20 MB</li>
    <li>Yahoo: 25 MB</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
