    tool to reduce file size, or <a href="/split-pdf" style="color: #2563EB;">Split PDF</a> into smaller chunks.
  </p>

  <h3>Problem: Can't edit PDF text</h3>
  <p>
    PDFs are designed to be read-only. To edit text, you need:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Adobe Acrobat Pro (paid)</li>
