    PDF/A is a specialized variant of PDF designed for long-term archival. It embeds all fonts and
    prohibits features that may not work in the future (like external links or encryption).
  </p>
  <p><strong>Use PDF/A for:</strong> Legal records, government documents, historical archives.</p>

